Nestled in the heart of Silicon Valley in the Thousand Oaks Community, this stunning home offers both luxury and functionality. Enjoy the open-plan living room with a wood-burning fireplace, hardwood floors, and French doors leading to the yard. The newly-remodeled kitchen features granite countertops, a double oven, and a breakfast bar. The dining area offers ample dinner space, while the separate family room is perfect for game nights. Each bedroom includes a closet and can be transformed into an office. The primary bedroom has its own ensuite for added privacy. Beautiful queen palms surround the flagstone patio and green grass; all cable lines are underground for a serene ambiance. Experience the comfort and convenience of a 2-car garage, storage shed, easy access to shopping, dining, major highways like Fwy 87 and 85, and two gorgeous parks.

This gorgeous 1,410 square foot home is comfort defined -- Situated on a large lot, lush-manicured landscape, and nature as your neighbor this home offers privacy, comfort, and is still minutes from Highway 85 and Silicon Valley.

The Gracious Floor Plan is ideal for entertaining, spacious living and lots and lots of room to have fun in -- You will want to invite your friends over every evening to enjoy the living space and the lush surroundings -- The interior of the home leads to the back yard entertainment area complete with large patio.

Adjacent to the kitchen is a spacious family room -- The living room has a beautiful open area with large glass views -- The dining area allows ample space for large gourmet meals.

This unique property is situated in Noddin Neighborhood with easy access to Highway 85 and Silicon Valley.

The kitchen includes plenty of cabinet space, newer granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, tile flooring, and a dining area. The spacious living room provides access to a private patio and storage closet. The primary bedroom is tucked away allowing for plenty of privacy and features a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. The ensuite bathroom features a shower over bathtub with brand-new glass shower doors. The guest bedroom also includes a walk-in closet and is conveniently located across from the guest bathroom and indoor laundry room. This complex offers two pools, two gyms, a recreation center, and a tropical retreat. Residents are just minutes away from downtown Campbell, Willow Glen, downtown San Jose, Valley Fair, and Santana Row. Easy access to all major freeways.

Enjoy modern living within the exclusive Villa Fontana gated community. This first-floor, end-unit condominium is located in the heart of Central San Jose and features modern finishes and an open-concept floor plan. The kitchen includes plenty of cabinet and pantry space, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. The main living area includes space for a dining area and provides access to a private patio and storage closet. The spacious primary bedroom is tucked away allowing for plenty of privacy and features new carpeting and a walk-in closet. The primary bathroom offers a double sink vanity, granite countertops, and a shower over the bathtub. Residents are just minutes away from downtown Campbell, Willow Glen, downtown San Jose, Rose Garden, Valley Fair, Santana Row and just a short walk to Los Gatos Creek Trail. Convenient access to Highways 280, 87, 880, and 101. Minutes from VTA. The community amenities include a private pool, fitness center, spa, and BBQ area. Residents are also assigned a parking space in the underground garage.

description: Move in and enjoy this beautiful single-story home tucked on nearly half an acre near Harker. Gorgeously updated single-story main home. The main home enjoys a large updated chef's kitchen with granite countertops, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Bright living and dining areas with views of the yard. Separate family game room. Large bedrooms. Tastefully updated bathrooms. Entertainer's dream, resort-like, private backyard with custom pizza oven, dining patios, bocce ball court and beautiful deck. Two car garage plus round-about drive. RV parking including dump station. Easy access to shops, freeways and expressways. Great schools. Gussie M Baker Elementary, Moreland Middle and Prospect High. Wow.

Large primary suite includes a generous walk-in closet with extensive shelving and a larger master bathroom. Luxury Pergo flooring, and carpet in the bedrooms. Easy access to the 87, 280, 85, and VTA. Enjoy dining establishments, grocery stores, and coffee shops in close proximity. Picturesque landscaping with an array of vibrant flowers throughout the year including drip system and sprinklers on timers. We're located on the perimeter of the park and have a small backyard.

***Come VIEW and MAKE an OFFER TODAY! Stunning land opportunity located in Santa Clara County, east of San Jose CA.  The 60+ ACRE PARCEL is positioned close to the Arroyo Bayo, Blumbago Canyon, and Long Gulch.  Zoned AR- Agricultural Ranchlands, the site allows for many different uses.  The purpose of Agricultural Ranchlands, also known as the AR district, is to preserve ranching, the natural resources, and the rural character of the areas to which it applies. Permitted uses include ranching or agriculture, low-intensity recreation, and mineral extraction.  In addition, very-low-intensity residential, commercial, industrial and institutional uses may also be allowed if they are sized to primarily serve the rural ranchland residents or are necessary for the enhancement and protection of the natural resources of the area. Privacy, nature, and convenience all at your finger tips. Come enjoy this private oasis for your next estate. Just minutes away from highway 680 and San Jose Country Club. Surrounded by exclusive homes, this parcel is ready for your dreams!

Large beautiful Mediterranean-style custom  home set on 10 acres. Home is in excellent condition. Property includes pipe corrals, stable and barn for horses, equipment and room for RV. Great property for family interested in riding horses. Private road off of S Koster back to house has little traffic and plenty of room to ride. Park-like yards are spacious and relatively low maintenance. Great place to raise a family with livestock and other hobbies. Easy access about two miles  from Highway 132, plenty of room for heavy equipment and big trucks. Great property for contractor, lots of room for storage and shops.

The secluded and private 5,733.29 acre Adobe Valley Ranch is located within the Mount Diablo Range on the south side of Del Puerto Canyon Road. It is 31 miles to Modesto, 49 miles to Stockton, 52 miles to Livermore, 56 miles to Merced, and 83 miles to San Jose. The ranch has been in the same family for 5 generations, running cattle for over 120 years. Currently, the Adobe Valley Ranch is used for cattle grazing and recreational purposes. It is fenced and crossed-fenced, running 100 pair year-round. Water on the ranch includes a year-round pond, Adobe and Lotta Creeks, and springs. The springs provide water to each of the buildings on the property as well as to the water troughs throughout the property. There is great hunting on the property with wildlife such as deer, wild boar, coyotes, foxes, mountain lions, and predators. Improvements include a main home & cabin, currently being rented, a workshop, a barn, and additional outbuildings. This a great opportunity for a cattle ranch or recreational property! In the Williamson Act.    Legend has it Joaquin Murrieta, the Robin Hood of the West / Robin Hood of El Dorado, would hold his horses in the Adobe Valley...

Incredible opportunity!!! 251 Acres of Agricultural Land in Prime Location. Property features a domestic well, agriculture well, and water tank. Electric pole and meter on property. Mineral rights makes this property extremely valuable. Conveniently located next to I-580, I-5, and HWY 132 in Tracy, CA. Just south of Tracy Golf & Country Club. Approx. 30 miles from Modesto, 35 miles from San Jose, 20 miles from Stockton and 60 miles from San Francisco. Future Possibilities are endless! APN 265-060-03(120 Acres) and APN 265-070-12 (131 Acres) Buyer to verify all Potential uses. Submit all offers!

Exceptional custom country home with peaceful views and all you can dream of in your next home - remodeled with impressive attention to detail with high end finishes throughout including a gourmet kitchen with huge center island, ooh la la stunning La Canche French gas range, great room with raised hearth fireplace. Owners suite and two bedrooms on first level - bonus room and guest bedroom and bath on second level (great for inlaws or nanny). All bathrooms upgraded! Multiple outdoor areas to enjoy - front courtyard, pool area and olive grove at side of house, built in BBQ, covered patio, two levels of decking and lots of views. So much to love about this property- you won't be disappointed!

You're going to fall in love with this one-of-a-kind property. It will leave you speechless. It proudly boasts beautiful main house with 3-bedroom, 2-bath, updated kitchen with open floor plan to an inviting family room with pellet stove. In addition, it has a manufactured 2-bedroom home that has updated with flooring, paint and amazing woodwork thru out. Come outside to a backyard that will take your breath away with very planned out features-play area, built in BBQ and bar area, pool, spa, and grass area. Entertainers special. In addition, it has a 2000sf warehouse. You really don't want to miss out on seeing this one of a kind. Workmanship shows what a nice

This remarkable home overlooking the 17th hole in the Eagle Ridge community is a beautiful place for you to call home!  Views galore from the back, with a sparkling pool. This home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths, 3,338 sq. ft. with a den or office.  Two story, downstairs bedroom with a full bath and access to the outside covered patio.  Over sized kitchen island, with an eat-in area, with a large walk-in pantry.  For entertaining,  a separate dining room adjoins the kitchen. You can relax in the  sitting area in the Master bedroom or sit out on the balcony outside Master, that looks out over all of Gilroy and beyond!  Four car garage with extra parking for guests. One of the newest developments in Eagle Ridge! This home has it all for any size family. Come live the good life!

Interested buyers please text message only. All calls are filtered to eliminate spam and solicitation.

A wonderful 95+/- acre parcel in the foothills of San Jose.  Multiple possible home sites have already been identified.  From the privacy, to the views, to the infrastructure that already exists this parcel is waiting for someone who wants to build their dream retreat.  Did we forget to mention the year round stream that runs through this property?  You will feel like you are in a different world when you venture to this amazing spectacle of nature. Don't miss this opportunity to own and live in the secluded hills below Mt Hamilton.  Couple this parcel with the adjoining 80+/- acres that has a cabin and workshop and you have an estate that you can develop and enjoy for generations to come.

Tucked back at the end of the street this great home has space for everything. It features a grand living room with a deck with views and a family room with a gas burning fireplace and a wet bar. In addition to the primary suite bedroom and 2 additional bedrooms on the main floor, there are 2 large rooms downstairs that can be used as additional bedrooms, an office, gym, etc. The interior of the home has also recently been painted, and also boasts new floors. There is also a big storage area underneath the house.

Nestled into the hills of West Dublin's desirable Cal Highlands neighborhood, surrounded by peaceful open space, rolling hills and oak trees is this updated 2-bedroom and 2-bathroom condo. Updates include new appliances, designer light fixtures, Nest thermostat, recessed lights and fresh paint in the bathrooms. Family room with cozy fireplace. 1-car attached garage offers extra storage and an electric vehicle charger. Enjoy the open-concept layout with the kitchen, dining room and family room all open to each other. Lots of natural light, backs up to open space. In addition to this beautiful home, you'll love the private back patio, great for relaxing or grilling. Only one block to 2 trailheads with views, community pool and hot tub. Great commute location, close to BART and freeways. Low HOA dues and a wonderful community! You won't want to miss this one!

The first level of this three-story home is host to the spacious open floorplan where the family room, dining and kitchen share a footprint. A secondary bedroom off the foyer is ideal for overnight guests or a home office. Three more bedrooms can be found upstairs, including the generous owner's suite with a private bathroom and walk-in closet. The versatile bonus room occupies the top level.

The Monterey is a single-story home of 2,003 square feet, ideal for those looking to downsize or growing families alike. The oversized entry-door leads to a front guest bedroom with walk-in closet perfect for an office or guest bedroom with privacy. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring 7 color options for granite slab or quartz kitchen countertops, 7 custom stain options of shaker style cabinets, premium stainless steel appliances, stunning tile flooring, and oversized pantry ? all standard features at Santana Ranch by Anderson Homes. The master bedroom features a private spa-like bathroom with separate shower and soaking tub, a large vanity, and a huge walk-in closet with built in organizers. Master and guest bathrooms include one of four standard piedrafina selections for vanities and master tub and shower surrounds. The oversized 2-car textured and painted garage features extra space for storage. Standard energy efficient features include drought tolerant landscaping, solar pre-wire, tankless water heater, and more.

Experience peaceful living in this beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath condo located in the desirable Cal Highlands neighborhood of West Dublin! With engineered flooring, plush carpeting, and a fireplace, this cozy home offers an open-concept layout with a recent kitchen remodel featuring quartz countertops and newer appliances. All bathrooms have been remodeled with updated features. Enjoy a fully fenced back patio and access to community amenities, including a pool and hot tub. Conveniently located near BART and freeways, this home is perfect for those seeking a great commute location. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity!
